Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved when preceded by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved when not preceded by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Total time from Completed + In Call to Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time between Completed + In Call and Completed + Resolved across all variants containing both activities
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average cycle time of Completed + Resolved in variants that include Completed + In Call versus variants that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time from Accepted + In Progress to Completed + Resolved in traces where Completed + In Call occurs versus traces where it does not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved grouped by country in cases that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Completed + Resolved in variants that contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time of Completed + Resolved following Accepted + Wait - User compared to when it follows Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total resolution time of Completed + Resolved in the most frequent variant containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time for Completed + Resolved after Accepted + Assigned in variants that also include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time between Completed + In Call and the next occurrence of Completed + Resolved within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time from case start to Completed + Resolved in traces featuring Completed + In Call versus those ending directly with Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle time of Completed + Resolved when it directly follows Completed + In Call versus when it follows Completed + Closed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time for Completed + Resolved in variants where Completed + In Call appears multiple times versus only once
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
